- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the trade-offs between quality and efficiency in machine learning algorithms. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with extracting information from large texts. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of powerful techniques such as data mining, machine learning, and natural language processing. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a less likely category, but it is possible as the paper discusses the impact of data set and evaluation technique on the results of the machine learning algorithms.
